name: HARD CANDY Dead Doe Handmade Wooden Keychain
description:
Sweeten up your wardrobe with Sugar & Spice DIY’s HARD CANDY Handmade Keychains! Charms so enticing you’ll want to take a bite. They're sweet, unique, and handmade by me. Pendants are hand painted and then designed using various different techniques & materials. Images protected under several layers of glossy sealer. 

Perfect for anyone in love with candy coated colors and wicked designs! Pendent measure about 1.5in and has a Dead Doe theme.

LOTS more for sale in my etsy store www.SugarAndSpiceDIY.etsy.com
